Introduces a new FFI-compatible `ExternalSigner` trait that allows users to provide their own signing implementations:

  ```rust
  // Create SDK with custom signer
  let signer = Arc::new(MyCustomSigner::new());
  let sdk = SdkBuilder::new_with_signer(config, signer)
      .build()
      .await?;
 ```

Also provided `DefaultExternalSigner` that is intialized with mnemonic to help users run their own signer on their secured environment without the need to implement the signer from scratch.

